name: Zonurus Couronneés
description:
--Fig.21-- 
Zonurus Couronneés is a creature from Majriti, and exoplanet located 43 light years away from Earth, orbiting the star Titawin. 
Zonurus are great beings that can reach up to 4 meters in height, and can spend their lives both grounded on earth as flying in the skies. They can protect from predators using their saw leaves and also their stings. Zonurus carry their young 2 at a time in big bags under their core, and can take them with for 2 years before they hatch.
